                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10198" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1525</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">319 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财数融江驱雾霭，华润启途耀星光 ——华润江中财务数字化焕新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial figures melt the river to drive away the fog and mist, CR starts the journey to shine the starlight -CRC Jiangzhong Finance Digital Transformation Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王丽南，王悦潼，丁琳琳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润江中制药集团有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务数字化转型；财务分析；创新驱动；业财一体化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Finance Digital Transformation, Financial Analytics, Innovation Driven, Business Finance Integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在当今时代，科技正以前所未有的速度迅猛发展，数字经济也随之蓬勃兴起，已然成为一股不可阻挡的时代潮流。本案例以华润江中制药集团的财务数字化转型为主题，系统阐述其在数字经济背景下推动财务管理体系全面革新的实践路径。面对医药行业政策密集调整、市场竞争日趋激烈以及内部管理效率亟待提升等多重挑战，华润江中积极响应国家政策导向，将财务数字化作为企业战略升级的重要引擎，逐步构建起涵盖战略规划、技术融合、流程重构与风险控制的全方位转型框架。在推进过程中，企业分阶段实施了一系列关键举措：首先通过升级SAP系统打通业务与财务数据链，推动财务处理自动化与成本管理精细化；随后建立财务共享服务中心，重构组织架构并优化费用报销、资金结算等核心流程，显著提升运营效率与协同能力；进而构建智能司库管理体系，加强资金统筹与风险预警，实现资金高效配置和稳健运营。
通过系统推进财务数字化转型，华润江中不仅实现了财务管理模式的深刻变革，还有力支撑了业务拓展与战略决策，为企业持续高质量发展注入新动能。本案例从体系构建、流程再造到成效赋能多层面总结其转型经验，为同类企业推进财务数字化提供了具有参考价值的实施路径与管理范式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In today&#39;s era, technology is advancing at an unprecedented pace, and the digital economy is flourishing accordingly, becoming an unstoppable trend of our times. This case study focuses on the financial digital transformation of China Resources Jiangzhong Pharmaceutical Group, systematically outlining its practical approach to driving comprehensive innovation in financial management systems within the context of the digital economy. Facing multiple challenges—including frequent policy adjustments in the pharmaceutical industry, intensifying market competition, and the urgent need to enhance internal management efficiency—China Resources Jiangzhong actively responded to national policy directives. It positioned financial digitalization as a key engine for strategic corporate upgrading, gradually establishing a comprehensive transformation framework encompassing strategic planning, technology integration, process reengineering, and risk control. During implementation, the company executed a series of phased initiatives: First, upgrading the SAP system to integrate business and financial data chains, driving automated financial processing and refined cost management. Subsequently, establishing a Shared Service Center for Finance, restructuring organizational frameworks, and optimizing core processes like expense reimbursement and fund settlement to significantly enhance operational efficiency and collaboration. Finally, building an intelligent treasury management system to strengthen fund coordination and risk early warning, achieving efficient capital allocation and stable operations.
Through systematic advancement of financial digital transformation, China Resources Jiangzhong has not only achieved profound changes in its financial management model but also provided robust support for business expansion and strategic decision-making, injecting new momentum into the company&#39;s sustained high-quality development. This case study summarizes its transformation experience across multiple dimensions—from system construction and process reengineering to outcome empowerment—offering valuable implementation pathways and management paradigms for peer enterprises pursuing financial digitalization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
